1
00:01:36,910 --> 00:01:40,160
[Born to Be Alive]

2
00:01:40,190 --> 00:01:43,190
[Episode 38]

3
00:01:45,620 --> 00:01:46,539
Zhacuo!

4
00:01:46,979 --> 00:01:47,950
Zhacuo!

5
00:01:54,500 --> 00:01:55,810
Really getting old.

6
00:01:55,830 --> 00:01:56,780
So slow.

7
00:02:02,540 --> 00:02:03,340
Manager Zhao.

8
00:02:03,540 --> 00:02:04,340
Manager Zhao.

9
00:02:06,860 --> 00:02:07,940
Zhacuo!

10
00:02:11,460 --> 00:02:12,320
What happened?

11
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:13,840
What happened?

12
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:15,000
Get to the hospital, fast.

13
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,170
He's lost too much blood.

14
00:02:16,170 --> 00:02:18,570
He won't make it
to the provincial capital.

15
00:02:23,150 --> 00:02:24,810
Is this how you handle things?

16
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,260
Wake up.

17
00:02:38,930 --> 00:02:39,660
Don't sleep.

18
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,250
What do we do?

19
00:02:46,250 --> 00:02:47,400
Drive faster!

20
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:48,690
No, I mean behind us.

21
00:02:49,340 --> 00:02:51,540
It's been following us for half an hour.

22
00:02:54,950 --> 00:02:55,760
Baima,

23
00:02:55,870 --> 00:02:57,130
are you at the pasture?

24
00:03:37,079 --> 00:03:37,560
Zhacuo,

25
00:03:37,810 --> 00:03:38,460
it's catching up.

26
00:03:38,460 --> 00:03:40,060
Keep driving! Keep driving!

27
00:04:02,870 --> 00:04:03,410
Get out.

28
00:04:06,020 --> 00:04:06,560
Friend,

29
00:04:06,580 --> 00:04:07,500
is something wrong?

30
00:04:07,500 --> 00:04:08,760
You ruined my pasture.

31
00:04:08,950 --> 00:04:09,750
What pasture?

32
00:04:09,870 --> 00:04:10,910
My pasture.

33
00:04:11,780 --> 00:04:12,340
I followed

34
00:04:12,340 --> 00:04:13,540
the tire tracks ahead of me.

35
00:04:13,540 --> 00:04:14,800
See? You've admitted.

36
00:04:14,870 --> 00:04:15,560
These tracks

37
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,510
were made by you.

38
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:17,149
No.

39
00:04:17,170 --> 00:04:18,829
They were made by the car ahead of me.

40
00:04:18,829 --> 00:04:19,630
The car ahead?

41
00:04:19,690 --> 00:04:20,190
Why didn't I

42
00:04:20,190 --> 00:04:21,130
see it?

43
00:04:21,220 --> 00:04:21,870
It just passed.

44
00:04:21,870 --> 00:04:22,690
Right there.

45
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,510
Ahead?

46
00:04:24,620 --> 00:04:25,370
Where ahead?

47
00:04:25,930 --> 00:04:26,920
I didn't see anything.

48
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:27,980
I only saw you.

49
00:04:30,590 --> 00:04:31,100
Hey, you,

50
00:04:31,100 --> 00:04:32,150
watch your attitude.

51
00:04:32,150 --> 00:04:33,270
You ruined our pasture,

52
00:04:33,270 --> 00:04:34,200
and you still...

53
00:04:37,190 --> 00:04:38,050
Is this enough?

54
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:41,800
Well...

55
00:04:43,250 --> 00:04:44,060
This pasture

56
00:04:44,300 --> 00:04:45,760
doesn't belong to just me.

57
00:04:46,220 --> 00:04:47,659
Ask my brothers here.

58
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,220
We're almost at the hospital.

59
00:05:31,340 --> 00:05:32,290
Hang in there.

60
00:05:38,930 --> 00:05:39,430
Hello?

61
00:05:39,830 --> 00:05:41,020
In the major hospitals in the city,

62
00:05:41,020 --> 00:05:42,180
I've arranged people to watch.

63
00:05:42,180 --> 00:05:42,980
Rest assured.

64
00:05:43,310 --> 00:05:44,000
Okay.

65
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:45,370
Keep a close eye.

66
00:05:45,500 --> 00:05:46,760
I'm coming right over.

67
00:05:47,540 --> 00:05:48,130
Wait.

68
00:05:51,620 --> 00:05:52,159
Bai Ji!

69
00:05:52,540 --> 00:05:53,120
Bai Ji!

70
00:05:53,280 --> 00:05:54,070
Come here, quick!

71
00:05:54,070 --> 00:05:54,950
Yunfei?

72
00:05:55,060 --> 00:05:55,520
Doctor!

73
00:05:55,620 --> 00:05:56,280
Who is this?

74
00:05:56,330 --> 00:05:57,180
Doctor!

75
00:05:57,200 --> 00:05:58,060
What happened?

76
00:05:58,190 --> 00:05:58,540
What happened?

77
00:05:58,540 --> 00:05:59,060
Doctor, come here!

78
00:05:59,060 --> 00:05:59,930
How did this happen?

79
00:05:59,930 --> 00:06:00,650
Hurry, hurry!

80
00:06:00,650 --> 00:06:01,310
Easy, easy!

81
00:06:02,060 --> 00:06:02,520
Come on!

82
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:03,160
Where is Mom?

83
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,090
Mom is upstairs.

84
00:06:04,090 --> 00:06:04,570
Go, go!

85
00:06:04,590 --> 00:06:05,190
Go get her!

86
00:06:05,210 --> 00:06:05,810
Go get her!

87
00:06:05,860 --> 00:06:06,260
Over here!

88
00:06:06,260 --> 00:06:07,320
Let's go! Let's go!

89
00:06:08,550 --> 00:06:10,050
[Tianduo Deji Hospital]

90
00:06:22,460 --> 00:06:23,370
Where is the emergency room?

91
00:06:23,370 --> 00:06:24,310
What are you doing?

92
00:06:24,310 --> 00:06:25,770
I'm asking you a question!

93
00:06:26,850 --> 00:06:27,340
Sorry,

94
00:06:27,370 --> 00:06:27,920
Miss.

95
00:06:28,370 --> 00:06:29,130
We are friends of the injured man

96
00:06:29,130 --> 00:06:30,000
who was just brought in.

97
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:30,980
We're very worried about him.

98
00:06:30,980 --> 00:06:32,180
His name is Zhao Yuji.

99
00:06:32,810 --> 00:06:33,850
The one with the knife wound, right?

100
00:06:33,850 --> 00:06:34,170
Yes.

101
00:06:34,659 --> 00:06:35,540
Turn left ahead.

102
00:06:35,540 --> 00:06:36,540
Treatment Room 3.

103
00:07:12,540 --> 00:07:13,600
What are you doing?

104
00:07:14,280 --> 00:07:15,460
Where is Zhao Yuji?

105
00:07:17,310 --> 00:07:18,540
Police! Drop the knife!

106
00:07:18,540 --> 00:07:18,950
Freeze!

107
00:07:18,950 --> 00:07:20,200
Let him go! Stand against the wall!

108
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:20,880
Ju!

109
00:07:20,970 --> 00:07:21,650
Save me!

110
00:07:22,830 --> 00:07:23,360
Bai Ji.

111
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:25,450
Are you okay?

112
00:07:25,530 --> 00:07:26,530
He has a knife!

113
00:07:29,130 --> 00:07:30,190
Did that scare you?

114
00:07:30,290 --> 00:07:30,760
Scare?

115
00:07:31,230 --> 00:07:31,730
Me?

116
00:07:32,610 --> 00:07:33,990
I've seen it all.

117
00:07:51,470 --> 00:07:52,640
Why do we meet here?

118
00:07:54,100 --> 00:07:55,100
Aren't you afraid

119
00:07:55,250 --> 00:07:56,340
of being seen?

120
00:07:58,130 --> 00:07:59,390
You really are scared.

121
00:08:00,030 --> 00:08:01,160
That's not like you.

122
00:08:03,810 --> 00:08:04,920
You said you'd ask your friends
in the province

123
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:06,250
to keep an eye on things.

124
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:07,560
Is this how they do it?

125
00:08:07,870 --> 00:08:08,620
Zhao Yuji is now

126
00:08:08,620 --> 00:08:10,150
in the provincial capital.

127
00:08:11,870 --> 00:08:13,620
It happened so suddenly.

128
00:08:15,810 --> 00:08:17,470
News didn't travel that fast.

129
00:08:18,660 --> 00:08:19,430
Besides,

130
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:21,450
before they left,

131
00:08:22,750 --> 00:08:24,440
I had already told you.

132
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,810
Your people failed to stop them.

133
00:08:28,620 --> 00:08:29,900
Why are you blaming me?

134
00:08:29,930 --> 00:08:30,990
Alright, alright.

135
00:08:31,150 --> 00:08:33,409
Let's not talk about useless things now.

136
00:08:33,630 --> 00:08:35,240
The key is what to do next.

137
00:08:36,980 --> 00:08:37,909
At the mine,

138
00:08:38,270 --> 00:08:39,470
should we scale back?

139
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:46,260
Lin.

140
00:08:46,940 --> 00:08:48,940
How can you laugh at a time like this?

141
00:08:50,790 --> 00:08:52,220
Why can't I?

142
00:08:54,150 --> 00:08:54,550
Come.

143
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:55,740
Look.

144
00:08:57,650 --> 00:08:58,380
Look at this.

145
00:08:59,340 --> 00:09:00,540
Look how well Tianduo

146
00:09:00,620 --> 00:09:01,750
has been developed.

147
00:09:02,770 --> 00:09:03,910
It's so beautiful.

148
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:06,120
The people
from the Discipline Inspection Commission

149
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:06,790
don't care

150
00:09:06,820 --> 00:09:08,220
how well you've built it.

151
00:09:10,990 --> 00:09:12,150
They only calculate

152
00:09:12,550 --> 00:09:13,870
what they want to.

153
00:09:24,710 --> 00:09:26,110
Let them calculate then.

154
00:09:29,220 --> 00:09:30,480
What are you afraid of?

155
00:09:33,740 --> 00:09:34,520
Zhao Yuji's matter

156
00:09:34,520 --> 00:09:35,830
was so many years ago.

157
00:09:36,250 --> 00:09:37,650
He signed the contract himself

158
00:09:37,650 --> 00:09:39,320
to sell the company.

159
00:09:41,220 --> 00:09:41,740
Later,

160
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:43,140
his leg was broken.

161
00:09:44,310 --> 00:09:46,640
It's just a charge of disorderly conduct.

162
00:09:48,030 --> 00:09:49,760
All the accusations against us

163
00:09:50,220 --> 00:09:51,840
are just his imagination.

164
00:09:52,030 --> 00:09:53,830
That case was settled years ago.

165
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:55,000
Digging it up now

166
00:10:00,580 --> 00:10:01,580
won't do any good.

167
00:10:11,330 --> 00:10:12,520
What about Jianshe?

168
00:10:15,940 --> 00:10:17,140
That's a minor issue.

169
00:10:18,370 --> 00:10:19,250
At most,

170
00:10:19,770 --> 00:10:21,240
I concealed from the organization

171
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:22,570
my child's information.

172
00:10:22,570 --> 00:10:24,630
It's just a disciplinary violation.

173
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:26,200
As long as what Xinhai

174
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,390
is doing now

175
00:10:28,940 --> 00:10:30,320
doesn't get exposed,

176
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:33,210
I have a way to get through this.

177
00:10:36,510 --> 00:10:37,840
Don't worry about that.

178
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:40,280
I know what I'm doing.

179
00:10:44,130 --> 00:10:45,140
That is the one thing

180
00:10:45,140 --> 00:10:46,470
I dread hearing you say.

181
00:10:48,170 --> 00:10:50,500
How many times have your people messed up?

182
00:10:51,190 --> 00:10:52,500
If it happens again,

183
00:10:54,540 --> 00:10:55,810
no one can save you.

184
00:11:25,910 --> 00:11:26,430
You...

185
00:11:26,550 --> 00:11:28,430
Why were you sitting in the dark?

186
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:29,840
Come here.

187
00:11:31,310 --> 00:11:31,720
I've bought

188
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:32,780
your plane ticket.

189
00:11:33,160 --> 00:11:34,000
It's to Beijing.

190
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:35,060
Once you get there,

191
00:11:35,300 --> 00:11:36,530
apply for a visa immediately.

192
00:11:36,530 --> 00:11:37,730
When you get the visa,

193
00:11:37,770 --> 00:11:38,720
go abroad immediately

194
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:39,720
and find Jianshe.

195
00:11:40,290 --> 00:11:41,090
What's wrong?

196
00:11:41,630 --> 00:11:42,890
Is Jianshe in trouble?

197
00:11:44,290 --> 00:11:45,600
Or is it our grandson?

198
00:11:50,770 --> 00:11:51,630
Wait a minute.

199
00:11:51,660 --> 00:11:52,490
Me, go abroad?

200
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:53,470
How can I leave

201
00:11:53,500 --> 00:11:54,360
just like that?

202
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:05,080
Song Ping?

203
00:12:15,210 --> 00:12:16,340
What does this mean?

204
00:12:20,530 --> 00:12:21,390
It means

205
00:12:25,050 --> 00:12:26,120
from now on,

206
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:28,460
your name is Song Ping.

207
00:12:34,980 --> 00:12:35,530
Lin.

208
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:39,200
Are you...

209
00:12:50,180 --> 00:12:51,780
Is there really no other way?

210
00:12:58,540 --> 00:12:59,390
As it stands,

211
00:13:03,250 --> 00:13:04,580
this is our only option.

212
00:13:14,050 --> 00:13:15,850
The flight is tomorrow morning.

213
00:13:15,940 --> 00:13:17,400
Go pack your bags quickly.

214
00:13:17,910 --> 00:13:19,110
Don't bring too much,

215
00:13:19,590 --> 00:13:20,970
to avoid attention.

216
00:13:22,530 --> 00:13:23,120
Go ahead.

217
00:13:43,230 --> 00:13:44,850
Is this my fault?

218
00:13:48,990 --> 00:13:49,940
Did I

219
00:13:51,820 --> 00:13:54,100
push you too hard sometimes?

220
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:02,510
No, how would...

221
00:14:03,010 --> 00:14:04,140
It's not your fault.

222
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:06,230
You did it for Jianshe,

223
00:14:07,170 --> 00:14:08,250
for this family.

224
00:14:13,310 --> 00:14:16,550
[Xining Huiren Hospital]

225
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:23,200
Since things are stable,

226
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:24,430
I'll go back today.

227
00:14:26,110 --> 00:14:27,030
There are still many patients in Tianduo

228
00:14:27,030 --> 00:14:28,130
waiting for me.

229
00:14:29,830 --> 00:14:30,370
Mom.

230
00:14:33,300 --> 00:14:33,970
Bai Ju and I

231
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,730
didn't mean to keep it from you.

232
00:14:37,160 --> 00:14:38,890
We just couldn't talk about it.

233
00:14:39,220 --> 00:14:40,020
I understand.

234
00:14:42,450 --> 00:14:43,180
Thanks, Mom.

235
00:14:44,990 --> 00:14:46,050
No need to thank me.

236
00:14:47,940 --> 00:14:48,670
I want to wait

237
00:14:48,720 --> 00:14:49,390
for the old man

238
00:14:49,390 --> 00:14:50,410
to recover a bit

239
00:14:50,570 --> 00:14:51,080
and explain the situation

240
00:14:51,080 --> 00:14:51,980
to the organization

241
00:14:51,980 --> 00:14:52,860
before going back.

242
00:14:52,860 --> 00:14:53,790
It's only right.

243
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:55,190
It's your job.

244
00:14:55,270 --> 00:14:57,130
You must finish what you started.

245
00:15:00,700 --> 00:15:01,960
It's happening again.

246
00:15:03,300 --> 00:15:04,540
Why do I always drop the ball

247
00:15:04,540 --> 00:15:05,740
at critical moments?

248
00:15:07,450 --> 00:15:08,850
Over 10 years ago,

249
00:15:11,430 --> 00:15:12,460
I went with Captain Duojie

250
00:15:12,460 --> 00:15:13,170
to Beijing.

251
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:16,200
In Beijing, we heard

252
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:18,660
something happened to the Mountain Patrol.

253
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:21,350
When we came back, everything had changed.

254
00:15:21,350 --> 00:15:22,350
But now,

255
00:15:24,460 --> 00:15:26,300
it's another critical moment.

256
00:15:29,870 --> 00:15:31,080
Why is it that every time

257
00:15:31,080 --> 00:15:32,800
Bai Ju needs me,

258
00:15:34,250 --> 00:15:34,840
I can't be

259
00:15:34,870 --> 00:15:36,170
by her side?

260
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:39,820
Put that way,

261
00:15:39,840 --> 00:15:41,240
I am pretty incompetent.

262
00:15:42,290 --> 00:15:43,490
Incompetent at what?

263
00:15:44,580 --> 00:15:45,500
Shao, I've noticed

264
00:15:45,500 --> 00:15:47,390
you're sharp

265
00:15:47,410 --> 00:15:48,810
and progressive at work,

266
00:15:49,030 --> 00:15:50,370
but when it comes to personal matters,

267
00:15:50,370 --> 00:15:51,700
you're so backward.

268
00:15:53,350 --> 00:15:54,310
I can see

269
00:15:54,340 --> 00:15:56,170
how Bai Ju feels about you.

270
00:15:56,400 --> 00:15:58,190
She likes you

271
00:15:58,790 --> 00:15:59,380
not because

272
00:15:59,380 --> 00:16:00,860
of what you do for her,

273
00:16:01,480 --> 00:16:02,000
but because

274
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:03,580
of who you are.

275
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:08,700
Don't think about anything else now.

276
00:16:08,700 --> 00:16:10,000
Just do your job.

277
00:16:11,540 --> 00:16:12,920
I think staying here

278
00:16:13,020 --> 00:16:14,420
and holding down the fort

279
00:16:14,670 --> 00:16:16,000
are what she wants most.

280
00:16:23,910 --> 00:16:25,650
Is the fish ready?

281
00:16:26,950 --> 00:16:27,550
Almost.

282
00:16:27,610 --> 00:16:28,490
Hurry up.

283
00:16:43,130 --> 00:16:43,600
Hurry.

284
00:16:45,840 --> 00:16:46,170
Mom!

285
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:47,000
They're back.

286
00:16:49,720 --> 00:16:50,220
Shao.

287
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:51,880
You're back.

288
00:16:54,890 --> 00:16:55,600
We're back.

289
00:17:03,610 --> 00:17:04,130
Mom.

290
00:17:20,510 --> 00:17:21,510
It's been a while.

291
00:17:22,300 --> 00:17:23,170
It feels like

292
00:17:23,310 --> 00:17:24,270
the whole family has not

293
00:17:24,270 --> 00:17:25,730
sat down for a meal in ages.

294
00:17:27,869 --> 00:17:29,400
We're not all here, though.

295
00:17:30,420 --> 00:17:31,180
True.

296
00:17:31,480 --> 00:17:32,390
Isn't Yan

297
00:17:32,420 --> 00:17:33,570
on duty today?

298
00:17:34,570 --> 00:17:35,070
Right.

299
00:17:35,350 --> 00:17:36,160
Next time, Bai Chun

300
00:17:36,160 --> 00:17:37,490
can't be absent either.

301
00:17:41,500 --> 00:17:42,090
Bai Ji.

302
00:17:42,360 --> 00:17:42,910
Come on.

303
00:17:43,250 --> 00:17:43,920
Taste

304
00:17:44,420 --> 00:17:45,280
the fish I made.

305
00:17:47,700 --> 00:17:48,590
Your sister went early in the morning

306
00:17:48,590 --> 00:17:49,850
to the market to buy it.

307
00:17:49,850 --> 00:17:50,780
It's very fresh.

308
00:17:54,310 --> 00:17:56,370
Do you really think I came here to eat?

309
00:17:57,270 --> 00:17:58,930
Like I'm desperate for a meal?

310
00:18:00,110 --> 00:18:01,140
What did we say on the way here?

311
00:18:01,140 --> 00:18:02,450
Didn't we agree to talk nicely?

312
00:18:02,450 --> 00:18:03,510
What are you doing?

313
00:18:03,790 --> 00:18:04,860
Weren't you curious on the way here

314
00:18:04,860 --> 00:18:05,500
about what happened

315
00:18:05,500 --> 00:18:06,430
at the hospital?

316
00:18:06,550 --> 00:18:07,200
Ask her.

317
00:18:07,510 --> 00:18:08,240
The person who knows best

318
00:18:08,240 --> 00:18:09,500
is sitting right here.

319
00:18:10,640 --> 00:18:12,010
Shao asked me the whole way.

320
00:18:12,010 --> 00:18:12,740
I didn't know

321
00:18:12,770 --> 00:18:13,830
what to tell her.

322
00:18:14,330 --> 00:18:15,680
All I know is that we helped a witness.

323
00:18:15,680 --> 00:18:16,800
Is this witness related

324
00:18:16,800 --> 00:18:17,710
to Xinhai?

325
00:18:20,350 --> 00:18:21,880
You and Brother-in-Law...

326
00:18:22,060 --> 00:18:23,660
You and ex-Brother-in-Law,

327
00:18:24,010 --> 00:18:25,220
what inside info have you found

328
00:18:25,220 --> 00:18:26,880
about Xinhai?

329
00:18:29,480 --> 00:18:30,220
Bai Ji.

330
00:18:30,900 --> 00:18:31,970
You're really

331
00:18:33,200 --> 00:18:34,420
putting me on the spot.

332
00:18:34,420 --> 00:18:34,970
Fine.

333
00:18:35,620 --> 00:18:36,090
Can this

334
00:18:36,120 --> 00:18:37,270
witness's testimony

335
00:18:37,270 --> 00:18:38,510
take down Xinhai?

336
00:18:40,570 --> 00:18:41,570
All I can say is,

337
00:18:42,610 --> 00:18:43,110
it's not

338
00:18:43,130 --> 00:18:44,050
that simple.

339
00:18:44,860 --> 00:18:46,140
That tells us nothing.

340
00:18:55,240 --> 00:18:56,410
I sent you info

341
00:18:56,440 --> 00:18:57,160
on 3 third-party

342
00:18:57,160 --> 00:18:58,490
testing agencies.

343
00:18:59,750 --> 00:19:00,550
Shao Yunfei and I

344
00:19:00,550 --> 00:19:01,810
picked them together.

345
00:19:02,460 --> 00:19:03,460
Look them over

346
00:19:03,900 --> 00:19:04,310
and see

347
00:19:04,330 --> 00:19:05,330
which one to pick.

348
00:19:06,440 --> 00:19:07,980
They are all authorities

349
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:09,260
on grass seed testing.

350
00:19:09,850 --> 00:19:11,050
We also discussed it.

351
00:19:11,190 --> 00:19:12,320
If later on,

352
00:19:12,440 --> 00:19:13,840
you have to pay a penalty,

353
00:19:14,860 --> 00:19:16,170
I'll sell my apartment

354
00:19:16,280 --> 00:19:17,220
to help you out.

355
00:19:19,740 --> 00:19:20,440
Ju,

356
00:19:21,230 --> 00:19:23,210
you're a leader of some sort.

357
00:19:23,550 --> 00:19:24,200
How can you be

358
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:25,480
so naive?

359
00:19:25,660 --> 00:19:26,520
Finding

360
00:19:26,550 --> 00:19:27,160
a testing agency

361
00:19:27,160 --> 00:19:28,760
won't solve the problem now.

362
00:19:28,790 --> 00:19:29,610
Let alone a third party,

363
00:19:29,610 --> 00:19:30,090
even a fourth

364
00:19:30,090 --> 00:19:31,120
or eighth party won't help.

365
00:19:31,120 --> 00:19:31,690
Bai Ji.

366
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:32,790
Save it.

367
00:19:33,050 --> 00:19:34,110
What are you doing?

368
00:19:36,090 --> 00:19:37,050
I finally get it.

369
00:19:37,700 --> 00:19:39,110
He just wants to screw me,

370
00:19:39,440 --> 00:19:40,320
screw us.

371
00:19:41,570 --> 00:19:42,270
I don't know

372
00:19:42,290 --> 00:19:43,790
what kind of backing he has.

373
00:19:43,790 --> 00:19:45,210
I only know one thing now—

374
00:19:45,640 --> 00:19:47,180
facing these people,

375
00:19:47,270 --> 00:19:48,360
if we keep retreating,

376
00:19:48,360 --> 00:19:50,020
we'll have nowhere left to go.

377
00:19:50,270 --> 00:19:51,540
Only by fighting back

378
00:19:51,800 --> 00:19:52,470
can we...

379
00:19:52,580 --> 00:19:54,270
might we protect our family

380
00:19:54,550 --> 00:19:55,960
and what's important.

381
00:20:00,640 --> 00:20:01,310
Anyway, I'm not good

382
00:20:01,310 --> 00:20:02,260
at big speeches.

383
00:20:03,250 --> 00:20:04,300
That old man

384
00:20:04,430 --> 00:20:05,560
is the best example.

385
00:20:17,420 --> 00:20:17,920
Mom.

386
00:20:19,140 --> 00:20:20,930
Why aren't you saying anything?

387
00:20:20,930 --> 00:20:22,300
You said everything

388
00:20:22,440 --> 00:20:23,890
I wanted to say.

389
00:20:23,910 --> 00:20:25,640
What else is there for me to say?

390
00:20:29,700 --> 00:20:30,660
Sure enough.

391
00:20:30,980 --> 00:20:33,180
Experience teaches better than words.

392
00:20:34,740 --> 00:20:35,470
That's good.

393
00:20:37,640 --> 00:20:38,570
You've grown up.

394
00:20:42,450 --> 00:20:43,580
Come on, eat.

395
00:20:43,900 --> 00:20:45,960
Ju made this fish especially for you.

396
00:20:50,350 --> 00:20:51,010
Thanks, Ju.

397
00:20:54,070 --> 00:20:54,550
Ju,

398
00:20:54,570 --> 00:20:55,170
let's eat.

399
00:21:04,360 --> 00:21:05,580
What's going on?

400
00:21:08,180 --> 00:21:09,940
Why didn't you call me for a meal?

401
00:21:09,940 --> 00:21:11,350
You're finally back.

402
00:21:13,090 --> 00:21:13,720
I'm back.

403
00:21:18,350 --> 00:21:19,320
It's ready?

404
00:21:19,350 --> 00:21:20,000
Yeah.

405
00:21:27,070 --> 00:21:28,460
Shao has good taste.

406
00:21:29,000 --> 00:21:30,990
These beans have a strong berry aroma.

407
00:21:30,990 --> 00:21:31,640
Really?

408
00:21:33,260 --> 00:21:34,850
You should learn how to make it.

409
00:21:34,850 --> 00:21:36,200
It's simple.

410
00:21:38,270 --> 00:21:38,770
You two are both

411
00:21:38,770 --> 00:21:39,980
fancy people from the big city.

412
00:21:39,980 --> 00:21:41,720
I don't have the energy to learn.

413
00:21:41,720 --> 00:21:42,650
It's just a cup of coffee.

414
00:21:42,650 --> 00:21:45,180
You're being prejudiced
against our region.

415
00:21:47,010 --> 00:21:47,810
What's wrong?

416
00:21:49,440 --> 00:21:50,480
What does Chun want to talk to you about?

417
00:21:50,480 --> 00:21:51,850
He's acting all mysterious.

418
00:21:51,850 --> 00:21:52,670
Don't pry.

419
00:21:53,230 --> 00:21:53,770
Finish your coffee

420
00:21:53,770 --> 00:21:54,460
and go home.

421
00:21:54,750 --> 00:21:55,490
It's hot.

422
00:22:02,960 --> 00:22:03,550
Chun.

423
00:22:04,980 --> 00:22:06,070
You'd better

424
00:22:06,660 --> 00:22:08,590
think it through before you speak.

425
00:22:10,140 --> 00:22:10,980
For some things,

426
00:22:10,980 --> 00:22:12,330
once you tell me,

427
00:22:13,590 --> 00:22:14,530
as a police officer—

428
00:22:14,530 --> 00:22:17,060
Xinhai is indeed involved
in illegal mining.

429
00:22:19,190 --> 00:22:20,520
During the inspection,

430
00:22:21,220 --> 00:22:21,850
someone tipped them off

431
00:22:21,850 --> 00:22:23,220
in advance.

432
00:22:25,480 --> 00:22:26,220
Meng Yaohui took us

433
00:22:26,220 --> 00:22:27,280
to forge the scene,

434
00:22:27,550 --> 00:22:29,280
covering up the illegal mining

435
00:22:29,820 --> 00:22:31,620
to deceive the inspection team.

436
00:22:32,560 --> 00:22:33,760
Do you have evidence?

437
00:22:35,350 --> 00:22:36,480
Is a witness enough?

438
00:22:37,270 --> 00:22:37,900
There's a miner

439
00:22:37,900 --> 00:22:38,980
who was injured at the site.

440
00:22:38,980 --> 00:22:40,180
He had an amputation.

441
00:22:41,740 --> 00:22:42,760
But Xinhai used money

442
00:22:42,760 --> 00:22:44,560
to suppress the whole incident.

443
00:22:44,820 --> 00:22:45,460
I'm not sure

444
00:22:45,460 --> 00:22:46,990
if he's willing to testify.

445
00:22:48,280 --> 00:22:48,850
We still need

446
00:22:48,850 --> 00:22:50,310
substantial evidence.

447
00:22:50,830 --> 00:22:51,560
For example,

448
00:22:51,800 --> 00:22:53,930
photos or videos of the scene,

449
00:22:54,350 --> 00:22:55,050
or sales records

450
00:22:55,050 --> 00:22:56,650
and financial transactions

451
00:22:56,680 --> 00:22:57,510
regarding the illegal mining.

452
00:22:57,510 --> 00:22:58,440
Anything works.

453
00:22:59,570 --> 00:23:00,110
Regarding this,

454
00:23:00,110 --> 00:23:01,080
Meng Yaohui, from the very beginning,

455
00:23:01,080 --> 00:23:02,610
set up off-the-book accounts.

456
00:23:02,610 --> 00:23:03,260
He established

457
00:23:03,260 --> 00:23:04,380
a separate finance office.

458
00:23:04,380 --> 00:23:05,220
It's not accounted for

459
00:23:05,220 --> 00:23:06,660
with the group's finances.

460
00:23:06,660 --> 00:23:07,290
And he never lets

461
00:23:07,290 --> 00:23:08,330
unauthorized personnel near it,

462
00:23:08,330 --> 00:23:09,200
including me.

463
00:23:14,010 --> 00:23:15,140
These past few days,

464
00:23:16,350 --> 00:23:18,150
I've been watching Meng Yaohui.

465
00:23:25,010 --> 00:23:26,340
When did you plant that?

466
00:23:51,930 --> 00:23:52,650
Mr. Meng.

467
00:23:56,630 --> 00:23:57,310
Mr. Meng.

468
00:24:00,460 --> 00:24:01,260
You're awake.

469
00:24:03,860 --> 00:24:05,290
The rain is really heavy.

470
00:24:05,310 --> 00:24:06,570
It hasn't stopped yet.

471
00:24:06,810 --> 00:24:08,810
As someone who has been to Bolamula,

472
00:24:10,670 --> 00:24:12,670
you shouldn't say things like that.

473
00:24:13,070 --> 00:24:14,530
Thanks for seeing me home.

474
00:24:15,750 --> 00:24:16,250
Bye.

475
00:24:18,050 --> 00:24:18,660
Bai Ju.

476
00:24:20,400 --> 00:24:21,730
You've been to Bolamula

477
00:24:23,820 --> 00:24:25,100
so many times.

478
00:24:26,740 --> 00:24:27,440
You've been through

479
00:24:27,440 --> 00:24:28,410
so much.

480
00:24:29,770 --> 00:24:31,300
Have you ever thought about

481
00:24:33,310 --> 00:24:34,570
living a good life?

482
00:24:38,180 --> 00:24:39,880
What counts as a good life?

483
00:24:41,640 --> 00:24:42,640
Looking forward.

484
00:24:44,140 --> 00:24:45,330
Choosing

485
00:24:46,000 --> 00:24:47,200
a smoother path,

486
00:24:48,140 --> 00:24:49,380
not a lonely one.

487
00:24:51,610 --> 00:24:52,940
But I don't feel lonely.

488
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:56,320
I used to have the Captain

489
00:24:56,800 --> 00:24:57,730
and friends.

490
00:24:59,960 --> 00:25:00,920
I still do now.

491
00:25:02,160 --> 00:25:03,110
To me,

492
00:25:04,680 --> 00:25:06,280
they've always been with me.

493
00:25:06,640 --> 00:25:07,770
They've never left.

494
00:25:08,900 --> 00:25:09,570
Besides,

495
00:25:10,570 --> 00:25:12,230
I'm not afraid of being alone.

496
00:25:16,230 --> 00:25:16,760
Goodbye.

497
00:25:31,950 --> 00:25:32,990
These few days,

498
00:25:33,660 --> 00:25:34,500
I've only seen

499
00:25:34,520 --> 00:25:36,000
his daily routine.

500
00:25:39,130 --> 00:25:40,460
You've done plenty.

501
00:25:41,530 --> 00:25:42,660
Leave the rest to me.

502
00:25:44,200 --> 00:25:44,840
Chun.

503
00:25:46,880 --> 00:25:48,480
If you really find evidence,

504
00:25:49,660 --> 00:25:50,720
what should you do?

505
00:25:51,770 --> 00:25:52,900
The forces behind Xinhai

506
00:25:52,900 --> 00:25:54,030
are complicated.

507
00:25:54,590 --> 00:25:56,590
You'll definitely get implicated.

508
00:25:57,820 --> 00:26:00,040
But my little sister is a police officer.

509
00:26:00,040 --> 00:26:01,430
She will protect me.

510
00:26:03,750 --> 00:26:04,870
But what if your little sister

511
00:26:04,870 --> 00:26:06,200
smashes your rice bowl?

512
00:26:06,840 --> 00:26:08,010
But I'm a stone.

513
00:26:09,960 --> 00:26:10,850
From the army

514
00:26:11,820 --> 00:26:12,820
to the coal mines,

515
00:26:13,160 --> 00:26:14,290
no matter where I am,

516
00:26:15,010 --> 00:26:15,680
I find

517
00:26:15,700 --> 00:26:16,720
my place.

518
00:26:17,900 --> 00:26:18,940
Wherever I'm needed,

519
00:26:18,940 --> 00:26:19,960
that's where I go.

520
00:26:20,400 --> 00:26:21,220
I know

521
00:26:22,110 --> 00:26:23,610
that right now, the one who needs me most

522
00:26:23,610 --> 00:26:24,480
is my sister.

523
00:26:25,530 --> 00:26:26,490
So I have to stand firmly

524
00:26:26,490 --> 00:26:27,580
by her side.

525
00:26:28,190 --> 00:26:29,490
No one can move me.

526
00:26:33,850 --> 00:26:35,110
I said you were a stone,

527
00:26:35,900 --> 00:26:37,160
not a brick.

528
00:26:38,650 --> 00:26:40,250
To be moved wherever needed.

529
00:26:46,240 --> 00:26:47,300
If you need me to be,

530
00:26:48,310 --> 00:26:49,530
I can also be a brick.

531
00:26:51,350 --> 00:26:52,610
After all these years,

532
00:26:53,490 --> 00:26:54,340
I know you are

533
00:26:54,360 --> 00:26:56,000
a responsible police officer.

534
00:26:56,000 --> 00:26:57,000
I just hope

535
00:26:57,590 --> 00:26:59,160
you can achieve your goal

536
00:27:00,400 --> 00:27:01,730
and stay safe.

537
00:27:03,290 --> 00:27:04,290
As for the future,

538
00:27:05,270 --> 00:27:06,470
whether you're alone

539
00:27:07,030 --> 00:27:08,050
or with someone,

540
00:27:10,170 --> 00:27:12,230
it'll be fine as long as you're happy.

541
00:27:17,030 --> 00:27:18,170
That second part

542
00:27:19,590 --> 00:27:21,140
sounds just like Mom.

543
00:27:25,720 --> 00:27:26,590
Mom loves you.

544
00:27:38,900 --> 00:27:39,750
And so do I.

545
00:27:45,230 --> 00:27:46,010
I know.

546
00:27:57,550 --> 00:27:58,000
Chun.

547
00:28:02,200 --> 00:28:02,700
I'm off.

548
00:28:04,100 --> 00:28:04,770
Off now?

549
00:28:14,310 --> 00:28:15,240
Is it good?

550
00:28:22,240 --> 00:28:22,810
All right.

551
00:28:22,810 --> 00:28:24,070
Stop drinking coffee.

552
00:28:24,210 --> 00:28:25,160
Have some fruit.

553
00:28:30,140 --> 00:28:30,980
Come clean.

554
00:28:31,710 --> 00:28:33,170
How much did you overhear?

555
00:28:34,470 --> 00:28:36,330
I wasn't eavesdropping. Really.

556
00:28:40,330 --> 00:28:41,000
Fine.

557
00:28:41,920 --> 00:28:43,610
I just caught the tail end.

558
00:28:43,630 --> 00:28:44,690
I didn't hear much.

559
00:28:52,380 --> 00:28:53,030
It's not some

560
00:28:53,030 --> 00:28:54,310
dirty secret.

561
00:28:54,420 --> 00:28:56,280
There's nothing to eavesdrop on.

562
00:28:56,510 --> 00:28:57,490
The fact that Chun likes you?

563
00:28:57,490 --> 00:28:58,860
I've known it for ages.

564
00:29:07,440 --> 00:29:08,850
You never felt it?

565
00:29:11,700 --> 00:29:12,070
I...

566
00:29:17,120 --> 00:29:17,860
Really.

567
00:29:18,850 --> 00:29:20,720
I just pretended not to know.

568
00:29:21,810 --> 00:29:22,340
Think about it.

569
00:29:22,340 --> 00:29:23,000
When we were kids,

570
00:29:23,000 --> 00:29:24,090
all those love letters

571
00:29:24,090 --> 00:29:25,020
boys gave you—

572
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:26,970
Chun confiscated them all.

573
00:29:27,300 --> 00:29:28,930
He never cared about me growing up.

574
00:29:28,930 --> 00:29:30,260
He only cared about you.

575
00:29:30,660 --> 00:29:31,610
I even secretly confronted him,

576
00:29:31,610 --> 00:29:33,140
asking why he was so biased.

577
00:29:33,310 --> 00:29:34,640
Just from his reaction,

578
00:29:35,180 --> 00:29:35,720
well,

579
00:29:36,130 --> 00:29:37,160
any idiot could tell

580
00:29:37,160 --> 00:29:39,350
it was because he liked you.

581
00:29:45,330 --> 00:29:47,160
You're so dense.

582
00:29:51,360 --> 00:29:52,290
What should I do?

583
00:29:53,220 --> 00:29:54,440
What is there to do?

584
00:29:54,460 --> 00:29:55,580
It's been so long.

585
00:29:55,610 --> 00:29:57,140
It's ancient history.

586
00:30:15,150 --> 00:30:16,340
I love you, too.

587
00:30:19,540 --> 00:30:20,540
Just like how Chun

588
00:30:20,970 --> 00:30:22,140
and Mom do to you.

589
00:30:25,720 --> 00:30:27,000
Don't get emotional yet.

590
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:28,750
I have my limits.

591
00:30:29,800 --> 00:30:31,100
Work is work,

592
00:30:32,310 --> 00:30:33,640
but safety comes first.

593
00:30:33,660 --> 00:30:34,230
Got it?

594
00:30:36,920 --> 00:30:37,530
Also,

595
00:30:38,170 --> 00:30:39,570
I have to take Han with me.

596
00:30:42,330 --> 00:30:43,410
That's not up to me.

597
00:30:44,570 --> 00:30:46,300
You have to ask if he's willing.

598
00:30:46,570 --> 00:30:48,100
He wouldn't dare to refuse.

599
00:30:49,400 --> 00:30:50,500
If he refuses,

600
00:30:51,250 --> 00:30:53,470
I'll put him in a chokehold

601
00:30:53,500 --> 00:30:55,030
and drag him away.

602
00:30:55,550 --> 00:30:56,420
You're choking me?

603
00:30:56,420 --> 00:30:57,900
Assaulting a police officer!

604
00:30:57,900 --> 00:30:58,200
I...

605
00:30:58,550 --> 00:30:59,480
Police assault!

606
00:30:59,660 --> 00:31:00,530
Go ahead and scream.

607
00:31:00,530 --> 00:31:01,880
Sue me.

608
00:31:03,130 --> 00:31:03,860
So annoying.

609
00:31:04,080 --> 00:31:05,280
You're so annoying.

610
00:31:31,880 --> 00:31:32,540
Why do you

611
00:31:32,570 --> 00:31:34,010
still drive this old car?

612
00:31:35,140 --> 00:31:35,790
Didn't Shao buy you

613
00:31:35,790 --> 00:31:36,920
a new one?

614
00:31:37,850 --> 00:31:38,940
She told you?

615
00:31:41,920 --> 00:31:43,420
The new car is at home.

616
00:31:44,230 --> 00:31:45,150
It's too nice.

617
00:31:45,180 --> 00:31:46,510
I can't bear to drive it.

618
00:31:47,700 --> 00:31:48,560
This old thing,

619
00:31:48,640 --> 00:31:51,170
patch it up,
and it'll run for a few more years.

620
00:31:53,980 --> 00:31:54,770
You two,

621
00:31:54,870 --> 00:31:55,750
breaking up one minute,

622
00:31:55,750 --> 00:31:57,550
and getting back together next.

623
00:31:57,720 --> 00:31:59,320
Are you playing us for fools?

624
00:31:59,940 --> 00:32:00,800
Impermanence.

625
00:32:01,980 --> 00:32:03,060
That's life.

626
00:32:03,620 --> 00:32:05,350
Don't give me that Zhacuo crap.

627
00:32:06,740 --> 00:32:07,420
Han.

628
00:32:08,590 --> 00:32:10,110
Since you've made up,

629
00:32:11,530 --> 00:32:12,790
as for future matters,

630
00:32:13,730 --> 00:32:14,590
you should stay out of them.

631
00:32:14,590 --> 00:32:15,220
Bai.

632
00:32:18,350 --> 00:32:19,150
I think impermanence

633
00:32:19,150 --> 00:32:20,410
means the unexpected.

634
00:32:21,980 --> 00:32:22,790
I thought I would

635
00:32:22,790 --> 00:32:23,990
be single all my life.

636
00:32:24,920 --> 00:32:26,420
Who knew at my age,

637
00:32:27,310 --> 00:32:28,500
I'd meet Bai Shao.

638
00:32:28,950 --> 00:32:30,090
You didn't meet her

639
00:32:30,120 --> 00:32:30,780
at this age.

640
00:32:32,320 --> 00:32:33,270
It was 18 years ago

641
00:32:33,270 --> 00:32:34,200
that you met her.

642
00:32:39,440 --> 00:32:42,240
I couldn't have imagined it
18 years ago either.

643
00:32:43,570 --> 00:32:45,700
We weren't going to take you on patrol.

644
00:32:47,350 --> 00:32:48,370
We all thought

645
00:32:48,680 --> 00:32:49,780
you wouldn't last.

646
00:32:51,380 --> 00:32:52,830
But you've kept at it

647
00:32:54,510 --> 00:32:55,380
until now.

648
00:33:03,510 --> 00:33:04,140
Bai,

649
00:33:05,490 --> 00:33:07,220
I have to keep working with you.

650
00:33:13,610 --> 00:33:14,180
Mom.

651
00:33:15,380 --> 00:33:15,880
Mom.

652
00:33:17,090 --> 00:33:17,620
Slow down. Slow down.

653
00:33:17,620 --> 00:33:18,530
Slow down. Slow down.

654
00:33:18,530 --> 00:33:19,950
Slow down. With your old arms and legs,

655
00:33:19,950 --> 00:33:21,950
you shouldn't carry so many things.

656
00:33:22,680 --> 00:33:23,570
You came back early

657
00:33:23,570 --> 00:33:24,700
without telling me.

658
00:33:24,720 --> 00:33:26,590
Good thing I bought a lot of groceries.

659
00:33:26,590 --> 00:33:27,900
Since you bought so many,

660
00:33:27,900 --> 00:33:29,300
are we expecting guests?

661
00:33:29,770 --> 00:33:31,110
I'm always prepared.

662
00:33:33,610 --> 00:33:33,980
Last time,

663
00:33:33,980 --> 00:33:35,590
when Bai came to visit,

664
00:33:35,760 --> 00:33:37,520
we had a really good chat.

665
00:33:37,980 --> 00:33:38,680
I heard.

666
00:33:40,040 --> 00:33:41,310
I can tell

667
00:33:41,620 --> 00:33:42,110
that she is

668
00:33:42,110 --> 00:33:43,640
a little interested in you.

669
00:33:44,440 --> 00:33:45,100
When a woman

670
00:33:45,110 --> 00:33:46,920
cares about a man's past,

671
00:33:47,010 --> 00:33:48,700
that says a lot.

672
00:33:49,370 --> 00:33:49,970
By the way,

673
00:33:51,020 --> 00:33:52,090
it seems a colleague of yours

674
00:33:52,090 --> 00:33:53,070
got into trouble.

675
00:33:53,070 --> 00:33:54,330
Bai is looking for him.

676
00:33:55,050 --> 00:33:55,770
Who?

677
00:33:56,160 --> 00:33:56,810
The one who picked you up

678
00:33:56,810 --> 00:33:58,290
to work in Guangdong.

679
00:33:58,680 --> 00:33:59,490
Wang.

680
00:34:02,880 --> 00:34:04,170
But I didn't tell her

681
00:34:04,260 --> 00:34:05,570
it had to do with you.

682
00:34:05,680 --> 00:34:07,630
Better to avoid trouble.

683
00:34:08,320 --> 00:34:09,179
How about that?

684
00:34:09,270 --> 00:34:10,790
I'm not that stupid, am I?

685
00:34:12,790 --> 00:34:14,580
Tell me earlier next time,

686
00:34:14,690 --> 00:34:15,949
so I can explain to her.

687
00:34:16,280 --> 00:34:17,719
What's there to explain?

688
00:34:17,880 --> 00:34:19,020
If she doesn't mention it,

689
00:34:19,020 --> 00:34:19,980
just let it go.

690
00:34:20,940 --> 00:34:22,610
Let's go. Time to eat.

691
00:34:25,380 --> 00:34:25,860
Here.

692
00:34:25,989 --> 00:34:27,170
Bye, Uncle Han.

693
00:34:27,190 --> 00:34:27,730
Get in the car, Zhuling.

694
00:34:27,730 --> 00:34:28,320
Bye.

695
00:34:38,090 --> 00:34:38,800
Auntie Wang.

696
00:34:38,800 --> 00:34:40,330
Bai, are you busy?

697
00:34:40,360 --> 00:34:41,400
No, I'm not. Go ahead.

698
00:34:41,400 --> 00:34:42,199
What's wrong?

699
00:34:42,730 --> 00:34:44,060
I was just about to cook,

700
00:34:44,170 --> 00:34:44,980
but Yaohui

701
00:34:45,030 --> 00:34:46,420
left in a hurry.

702
00:34:47,130 --> 00:34:48,650
He's gone to Dingduo County again?

703
00:34:48,650 --> 00:34:49,290
Yes.

704
00:34:49,949 --> 00:34:51,679
My intuition is usually right.

705
00:34:51,830 --> 00:34:53,300
He didn't have any plans.

706
00:34:53,330 --> 00:34:54,989
He just decided to go on a whim.

707
00:34:55,750 --> 00:34:57,480
Maybe he's gone to see someone.

708
00:34:59,230 --> 00:35:00,830
Okay, I understand, Auntie.

709
00:35:01,310 --> 00:35:02,080
I'll find him

710
00:35:02,110 --> 00:35:03,300
and get to the bottom of it.

711
00:35:03,300 --> 00:35:04,180
Okay, okay.

712
00:35:04,880 --> 00:35:05,810
Thanks, Auntie.

713
00:35:26,720 --> 00:35:27,420
Drink up.

714
00:35:29,760 --> 00:35:30,890
Where are you going?

715
00:35:30,940 --> 00:35:32,160
To patrol the mountain.

716
00:35:32,160 --> 00:35:33,360
Patrol the mountain?

717
00:35:33,590 --> 00:35:34,650
Just the two of you?

718
00:35:35,360 --> 00:35:36,510
Even if I'm the only one left,

719
00:35:36,510 --> 00:35:37,770
I still have to patrol.

720
00:35:39,460 --> 00:35:40,460
He's confused.

721
00:35:42,740 --> 00:35:44,340
He still thinks it's the 90s.

722
00:38:53,380 --> 00:38:54,420
I won! I won!

723
00:38:54,440 --> 00:38:54,960
Look.

724
00:38:55,480 --> 00:38:56,210
I'm amazing.

725
00:38:56,230 --> 00:38:56,780
You each have to

726
00:38:56,780 --> 00:38:57,940
buy me a popsicle.

727
00:38:57,960 --> 00:39:00,380
Aren't you afraid
of getting a stomachache?

728
00:39:00,380 --> 00:39:01,150
A bet is a bet.

729
00:39:01,170 --> 00:39:02,440
It's not my fault you didn't win.

730
00:39:02,440 --> 00:39:03,280
If you're so good,

731
00:39:03,280 --> 00:39:04,610
go buy a lottery ticket.

732
00:39:10,180 --> 00:39:11,780
He said his start-up failed,

733
00:39:11,900 --> 00:39:13,520
but actually,
he loves buying lottery tickets,

734
00:39:13,520 --> 00:39:15,450
hoping to strike it rich every day.

735
00:39:47,810 --> 00:39:49,210
Excuse me. Excuse me.

736
00:39:57,440 --> 00:39:58,040
Wang Jian.

737
00:39:59,200 --> 00:40:00,130
What do you want?

738
00:40:00,460 --> 00:40:01,170
Who are you?

739
00:40:01,560 --> 00:40:02,540
Sorry.

740
00:40:02,570 --> 00:40:04,830
I mistook you for someone else. Apologies.

741
00:40:04,830 --> 00:40:05,960
Weirdo.

742
00:40:27,300 --> 00:40:28,010
Mr. Meng.

743
00:40:28,600 --> 00:40:30,200
You've got the wrong person.

744
00:40:30,510 --> 00:40:31,540
No, I haven't.

745
00:40:31,620 --> 00:40:32,680
It is you, Mr. Meng.

746
00:40:35,110 --> 00:40:36,570
It really is you, Mr. Meng.

747
00:40:38,190 --> 00:40:39,590
Is something the matter?

748
00:40:40,170 --> 00:40:41,160
Meeting you here

749
00:40:41,190 --> 00:40:42,450
is such a coincidence.

750
00:40:43,120 --> 00:40:43,770
As the saying goes,

751
00:40:43,770 --> 00:40:45,430
fate brings people together.

752
00:40:46,070 --> 00:40:47,670
Is this a chance encounter?

753
00:40:48,220 --> 00:40:49,210
I have things to do.

754
00:40:49,210 --> 00:40:49,940
I'm leaving.

755
00:40:51,220 --> 00:40:52,750
Don't be in a rush, Mr. Meng.

756
00:40:53,200 --> 00:40:54,480
Regarding the proposal

757
00:40:54,480 --> 00:40:55,700
we talked about before,

758
00:40:55,700 --> 00:40:57,500
we've discussed it thoroughly,

759
00:40:57,720 --> 00:40:59,320
and we all think it's pretty good.

760
00:40:59,320 --> 00:41:00,120
That's right.

761
00:41:00,930 --> 00:41:01,350
I heard

762
00:41:01,380 --> 00:41:02,910
you can arrange a job for me,

763
00:41:03,200 --> 00:41:04,860
and the salary is negotiable.

764
00:41:34,780 --> 00:41:35,360
How did that person

765
00:41:35,360 --> 00:41:36,450
claiming to be Wang Fumin's friend

766
00:41:36,450 --> 00:41:37,660
contact you?

767
00:41:39,050 --> 00:41:39,940
Days after you

768
00:41:39,960 --> 00:41:41,370
visited my house

769
00:41:41,460 --> 00:41:42,160
last time,

770
00:41:42,460 --> 00:41:43,790
he called me.

771
00:41:44,230 --> 00:41:45,490
He said his surname is Chen,

772
00:41:45,490 --> 00:41:47,240
and that he's an old colleague of my dad,

773
00:41:47,240 --> 00:41:49,570
who went abroad
to work with him back then.

774
00:41:50,110 --> 00:41:51,770
I didn't believe him at first,

775
00:41:52,090 --> 00:41:53,570
but he accurately stated

776
00:41:53,590 --> 00:41:54,590
my dad's

777
00:41:54,740 --> 00:41:55,690
remittance times

778
00:41:55,690 --> 00:41:56,950
and amounts back then.

779
00:41:57,030 --> 00:41:58,070
He also said my dad

780
00:41:58,090 --> 00:41:59,690
took good care of him abroad,

781
00:42:00,150 --> 00:42:02,410
and that he wanted to repay the kindness.

782
00:42:03,050 --> 00:42:04,850
So he paid off your debts for you.

783
00:42:05,300 --> 00:42:06,050
He put another 500,000

784
00:42:06,050 --> 00:42:06,940
into your card.

785
00:42:11,830 --> 00:42:12,790
Did you ask him

786
00:42:13,600 --> 00:42:15,000
where your father is now?

787
00:42:15,380 --> 00:42:16,190
I did.

788
00:42:16,780 --> 00:42:18,350
He said he didn't know either.

789
00:42:18,350 --> 00:42:19,380
He said it was because

790
00:42:19,380 --> 00:42:20,330
he couldn't find my father

791
00:42:20,330 --> 00:42:21,980
that he came to me.

792
00:42:23,170 --> 00:42:25,050
He also bought me a house

793
00:42:25,150 --> 00:42:26,280
in Dingduo County.

794
00:42:26,800 --> 00:42:27,630
He said he wanted to help me

795
00:42:27,630 --> 00:42:29,320
improve my living conditions.

796
00:42:29,320 --> 00:42:30,140
So generous.

797
00:42:30,920 --> 00:42:32,920
What are the plans for the next step?

798
00:42:33,570 --> 00:42:34,800
For the future,

799
00:42:34,900 --> 00:42:36,530
he said he'd send me abroad

800
00:42:36,760 --> 00:42:38,360
and arrange a good job for me.

801
00:42:38,900 --> 00:42:39,610
How do you contact

802
00:42:39,610 --> 00:42:40,940
this guy surnamed Chen?

803
00:42:41,550 --> 00:42:42,320
Just...

804
00:42:42,650 --> 00:42:43,430
by phone.

805
00:42:44,170 --> 00:42:44,920
Haven't you met him in person?

806
00:42:44,920 --> 00:42:45,470
No.

807
00:42:45,650 --> 00:42:47,400
He sounded like he was

808
00:42:47,430 --> 00:42:49,020
in his thirties or forties.

809
00:42:51,560 --> 00:42:52,960
Do you know Zhou Fusheng?

810
00:42:54,350 --> 00:42:55,120
Who?

811
00:42:55,540 --> 00:42:57,150
The owner of the account
that sent you money

812
00:42:57,150 --> 00:42:58,410
is named Zhou Fusheng.

813
00:42:58,510 --> 00:42:59,780
A migrant worker from the south.

814
00:42:59,780 --> 00:43:00,960
He has admitted
that he was short of money,

815
00:43:00,960 --> 00:43:02,630
so he sold his ID card to someone else.

816
00:43:02,630 --> 00:43:03,550
Why do you think

817
00:43:04,100 --> 00:43:05,900
this Chen guy used a fake identity

818
00:43:05,900 --> 00:43:06,950
to get close

819
00:43:06,970 --> 00:43:07,800
to you?
